# This app needs NO environment variables to run or deploy.
#
# It is Bring-Your-Own-Key: visitors paste their own Bright Data token in the UI,
# the Worker forwards it per request, and nothing is stored. The dataset ID is
# hard-coded in src/worker.js. There is no .env for the app to read.
#
# The variable below is ONLY for running the raw API example in the README from
# your own terminal — the app itself never reads it.
# Get a token: https://brightdata.com -> account settings -> API keys
BRIGHT_DATA_API_TOKEN=your-bright-data-token-here
